UID:GzB1Ddh5Tq3eP4oGP3GPJ
SUMMARY:BATTLE OF THE BADGES
DTSTAMP:20260623T142644Z
DTSTART:20260630T140000Z
DESCRIPTION:? BATTLE OF THE BADGES — JUNE 30\, 2:00PM–8:00PM \nCome donate 
	blood and cast your vote — HPD or HFD\, who will win? The Battle of the Ba
	dges blood drive takes place Tuesday\, June 30 from 2:00–8:00pm at the His
	toric Houston Heights Fire Station (107 W. 12th St) as part of the city-wi
	de competition running June 28–July 5. Every successful donor receives a s
	pecial edition baseball cap and a FREE $25 Donor Rewards Store gift card! 
	Use sponsor code HHA8 when scheduling. Click below to sign up and help you
	r team win! \n  \nhttps://www.commitforlife.org/donor/schedules/drive_sche
